    {"scene_type": "agree", "content": "这个主意不错！我喜欢！", "mood": "excited", "weight": 4},
    {"scene_type": "agree", "content": "嗯…确实是这样。", "mood": "neutral", "weight": 2},
    {"scene_type": "disagree", "content": "哼，我可不这么想。", "mood": "tsundere", "weight": 3},
    {"scene_type": "disagree", "content": "喂喂喂，你这是什么逻辑？", "mood": "annoyed", "weight": 3},
    {"scene_type": "disagree", "content": "不对不对，应该是这样的——", "mood": "serious", "weight": 3},
    {"scene_type": "morning", "content": "早啊！今天也要精神满满地练剑！", "mood": "happy", "weight": 4},
    {"scene_type": "morning", "content": "哼…早。我还没睡醒呢。", "mood": "bored", "weight": 3},
    {"scene_type": "morning", "content": "早安！早餐吃什么？琼实鸟串吗？", "mood": "excited", "weight": 3},
