    {"scene_type": "night", "content": "哼，谁要跟你说晚安了！…好吧，晚安。", "mood": "tsundere", "weight": 3},
    {"scene_type": "night", "content": "我要去睡觉了。梦里说不定能遇到好剑呢。", "mood": "happy", "weight": 3}
